mainPackage

Class ExternalVoxelizedWorld

  • java.lang.Object
    • mainPackage.VoxelizedObject
      • mainPackage.ExternalVoxelizedWorld
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ExternalVoxelizedWorld
extends VoxelizedObject
    This object represents the external object of the object. It is a VoxelizedObject with all values DosiVox need to performs. That object, if sub-voxelized detector is setted, has the InternalVoxelizedWorld.
    Author:
    Guitard Alan
    See Also:
    VoxelizedObject, InternalVoxelizedWorld, Serialized Form
